{"tid":2284873,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有時見到連登班炒狗就覺得好笑","createTime":"2020-11-13T15:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T09:08:02.000Z","uid":43557,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb2e7093b976673a4ec809187141fe3ba7913b8","tid":2284873,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫班先達狗講野<br />\n但係見到今年連登班炒狗就覺得好笑<br />\nIphone呢一兩年已經係炒唔起<br />\n係今年疫情問題炒返起少少<br />\n不過都一定冇高峰期果陣咁誇張<br />\n連登班炒狗就以為pro好似炒返起<br />\n就以為pro max都一定起碼炒到+1000~2000<br />\n到真係出現過+1000 之後成班就以為可以再炒高d<br />\n點知sh到渣都冇 <br />\n自己唔識判斷淨係識聽人講sh<br />\n炒燶左又屌柒先達狗<br />\n係炒iphone個po見過最撚好笑既reply就係話唔想益班先達狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇佢地俾d水位同你收等係連登義海區等人收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一係咁叻自己運上去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班先達狗起碼都有成本 租鋪 運上去等等<br />\n你地成班炒狗咩成本都冇係度屌柒人地<br />\n每部+3000好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估仲係以前？<br />\n不過呢個都唔係最大問題<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">你地都係一班炒狗咋柒頭</span></span> <br />\n你地跟本冇資格屌人<br />\n你班撚樣都係搞撚到自用撚要等<br />\n要屌都係自用撚屌先啦"},{"pid":"07e084626dcbd60fbef3135cbc43cd7f48135b8f","tid":2284873,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"炒撚完未成班乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6627bde60d3ec751f45def352848ff08dc873177","tid":2284873,"uid":43557,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"07e084626dcbd60fbef3135cbc43cd7f48135b8f","tid":2284873,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"炒撚完未成班乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited